                    },
                    "body": "@Eric ZF1 must be compatible with PHP 5.2.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=intiilapa",
                        "name": "intiilapa",
                        "displayName": "Beno\u00eet Durand",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-06-06T21:06:04.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-06-06T21:06:04.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/47007",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I'm going to move this issue to the ZF2 issue tracker, as LSB is only available in PHP >= 5.3, and ZF1's minimum version is 5.2.6. There may be other ways to potentially support this in 5.2, but the proper way is using LSB.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-06-06T21:15:21.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-06-06T21:15:21.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/47011",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=intiilapa",
                        "name": "intiilapa",
                        "displayName": "Beno\u00eet Durand",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "All factory methods of logger, writers, filtesr, and formatters are being refactored within ZF2.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=intiilapa",
                        "name": "intiilapa",
                        "displayName": "Beno\u00eet Durand",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-06-07T04:55:52.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-06-07T04:55:52.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/47013",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=eandre",
                        "name": "eandre",
                        "displayName": "Eric Andre",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Okay, i dont respect the compatibility. So thanks for regarding this issue.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=eandre",
                        "name": "eandre",
                        "displayName": "Eric Andre",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-06-07T08:55:23.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-06-07T08:55:23.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/48319",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=intiilapa",
                        "name": "intiilapa",
                        "displayName": "Beno\u00eet Durand",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Once the common API (puggable, configurator, etc.) will have been decided for the core components of ZF2, Logger will adopt it. Being able to extend any core component is a requirement for this solution.\r\n\r\nIt is also possible to consider including events in order to customize the logging.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=intiilapa",
                        "name": "intiilapa",
                        "displayName": "Beno\u00eet Durand",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-09-03T08:26:39.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-09-03T08:26:39.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/49297",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=evan.pro",
                        "name": "evan.pro",
                        "displayName": "Evan Coury",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I see no reason for us to wait until after we refactor for the new configuration style to make this change. LSB is the correct way to handle a situation like this, and it's a simple enough change. I went ahead and issued a PR for this: https:\/\/github.com\/zendframework\/zf2\/pull\/680",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=evan.pro",
                        "name": "evan.pro",
                        "displayName": "Evan Coury",
                        "active": true
                    },
